<li id="cite_note-164"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-164">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Al-Banna, Hasan, <i>Five Tracts of Hasan Al-Banna, (1906–49): A Selection from the "Majmu'at Rasa'il al-Imam al-Shahid Hasan al-Banna"</i>, Translated by Charles Wendell. Berkeley, CA, 1978, pp. 150, 155;</span>
